    Element is the base class for Chanson and LivreAudio.
    ElementList
    ElementList is the class containing all elements in a list.
    LivreAudio
    LivreAudio is an audio book object in the librairy.

    A Playlist object contains a list of songs and audio books from the librairy.
    PlaylistList
    PlaylistList is the class containing all playlists in a list.
    UserList
    UserList is the parent class of ElementList, AlbumList and PlaylistList.
